flowchart TD
    A[Select highest-priority unblocked item] --> B{Streaming UI available?}
    B -->|No: backend has only POST /api/agents/run| C[Keep streaming task blocked in plan]
    B -->|Yes| Z[Implement streaming client]

    C --> D[Implement P0 visual-theme baseline]
    D --> E[Apply cyberpunk CSS tokens\n dark base + neon accent + panel surfaces]
    E --> F[Add explicit theme markers\n data-theme=cyberpunk + neon-action classes]
    F --> G[Add deterministic frontend render test\n validates themed markers and section surfaces]

    G --> H[Run fresh infra cycle\n docker compose down -v --rmi all\n build\n up -d]
    H --> I[Run required checks]
    I --> I1[Health endpoint PASS]
    I --> I2[Backend pytest PASS]
    I --> I3[Frontend tests PASS]
    I --> I4[Frontend typecheck/build PASS]

    I4 --> J[Update IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md\n mark visual-theme done\n keep streaming blocked]
    J --> K[Write .loop-commit-msg]

    classDef blocked fill:#3b0d14,stroke:#ff698c,color:#ffd7df;
    class C blocked;
